snippet.title: The Breakout Project
snippet.description:
The Breakout Project is Canada’s newest social innovation festival purposefully designed to
kickstart world-changing projects over the course of 48 continuous hours. With renowned
speakers, an online collaboration platform, and a series of engagement strategies, the event was
created to bring the resources together to kick start the transition of social innovation projects
from ideation to measured impact within 365 days.

The Breakout Project’s mission is to scale social good businesses quickly. The world’s greatest
innovators require massive amounts of four key ingredients:
   1. Talented Human Resources
   2. Organization Awareness
   3. Key Industry Connections
   4. Financial Capital

The Breakout Project was designed to attract these four ingredients on a massive scale, to allow
social innovation projects to scale quickly from concept to demonstrable impact.

Learn more at: https://www.thebreakoutproject.com
